Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.60,0:03:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,响
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.86,0:03:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个伤...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我造成的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.26,0:03:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托妳的福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢妳 未来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,响？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.70,0:03:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我救了妳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.18,0:03:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是妳救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,响？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个装备释放出的光线
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.68,0:03:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以分解来自圣遗物的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并使其完全无效化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果就是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.72,0:03:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只两人的装备被解除
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:04:01.42,Default-eng2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(683.333,650)}Gungnir
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:04:01.42,Default-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(683.333,650)}Gungnir
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:04:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,侵蚀着响身体的永恒之枪也被分解了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小日向妳强烈的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拯救了濒临死亡的立花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.94,0:04:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的有困难的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未来妳果然帮助了我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢妳！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.83,0:04:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帮助了响...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.52,0:04:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.47,0:04:31.25,Default-eng2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(720,650)}Frontier
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.47,0:04:31.25,Default-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(720,650)}Frontier
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.47,0:04:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FIS终究还是让疆域浮上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真正的战斗正要开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FIS的企图
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就由我一个人来消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克莉丝呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到沉睡在海底是这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是妳所盼望的新天地唷！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,背叛同伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是想要加入我们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是最好的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要击垮某股力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能以更强大的力量压制
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.86,0:05:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只希望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.19,0:05:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战斗范围不要继续扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想阻止无辜生灵被屠杀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.75,0:05:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的相信与我们合作就能阻止战争扩大吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来没被相信呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.49,0:05:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是不爽我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随时可以从背后射杀在前线作战的我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是电力室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.24,0:06:22.76,Default-eng2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(513.333,650)}Nephilim
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.24,0:06:22.76,Default-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(513.333,650)}Nephilim
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.24,0:06:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,堕落者的心脏居然...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即便只剩心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吞噬圣遗物的特性还是没变
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真下流呀...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这份能量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:41.68,Default-eng2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(596.667,650)}Frontier
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:41.68,Default-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(596.667,650)}Frontier
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让疆域苏醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.08,0:06:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就先到舰桥了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜丝塔夏教授也
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.95,0:06:51.47,Default-eng2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(790,650)}Frontier
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.95,0:06:51.47,Default-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(790,650)}Frontier
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.95,0:06:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请您到操纵室照料疆域了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:06:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教授的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无法拯救弱者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:05.52,Default-eng2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(626.667,650)}Frontier
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:05.52,Default-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(626.667,650)}Frontier
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有疆域的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本救无法拯救任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连调都无法拯救！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望拯救她们...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她这样说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.69,0:07:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望能阻止盲目暴走的伙伴们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好好静养不行吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直坐立不安...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她听说克莉丝不在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就怎么样都想过来...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然响与克莉丝脱离战斗的确严重影响作战进度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翼没受到重伤是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.56,0:07:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都躲过致命伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.68,0:07:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身手真好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躲开了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.98,0:07:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种状况怎么可能闪避雪音的攻击？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.52,0:07:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也就是说...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.93,0:07:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:02.03,Default-eng2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(726.667,650)}Frontier
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:02.03,Default-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(726.667,650)}Frontier
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上要接近疆域了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.25,0:08:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,LiNKER罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.13,0:08:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混入圣遗物后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:26.86,Default-eng2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(476.667,650)}Nephilim
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:26.86,Default-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(476.667,650)}Nephilim
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,经由堕落者细胞所合成的LiNKER
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想试试呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿他们来小试身手也不错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳认为呢？ 玛丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:02.91,Default-eng2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,650)}Frontier
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:02.91,Default-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,650)}Frontier
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果疆域是史前文明时代支配者的遗产的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就会是异端技术的融合体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对应月球冲击的手段也一定有...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.83,0:09:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也无法回头了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合为一体后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.38,0:09:21.44,Default-eng2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,650)}Frontier
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.38,0:09:21.44,Default-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,650)}Frontier
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.38,0:09:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疆域的能量分布都非常清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.21,0:09:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样很足够大闹一场
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太急了 教授
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.78,0:09:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.60,0:09:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大解除！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.88,0:10:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教授那份膨胀的欲望...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在闹大之前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必须找到可靠的异端技术阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大范围的陆地隆起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.54,0:10:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的正下方也升起了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作战本部的命令下达
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是要镇压他们...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本没听过那种东西啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.24,0:10:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,激动到眼镜快要掉了～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.79,0:11:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能够控制重力的界限就是这样了吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能救赎人类的力量吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能够蹂躏他们的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.43,0:11:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样我也能成为英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.66,0:11:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成为这颗星球最终的英雄啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.47,0:11:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是大规模地壳变动的海域所发生的军舰冲击事故
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美国军舰一瞬间就...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.76,0:11:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小寺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:11:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种事件...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:11:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道跟立花她们...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该不会有关系啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来从下面打捞出好东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.44,0:12:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,量测结果出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下方地面的上升
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因为向月球抛出像锚的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.64,0:12:15.16,Default-eng2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(560,650)}Frontier
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.64,0:12:15.16,Default-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(560,650)}Frontier
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.64,0:12:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而把疆域拉上来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.56,0:12:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.28,0:12:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不只是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么用力一拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不小心又把月球拉近了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.70,0:12:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把月球...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.86,0:12:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是说下坠加速了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.46,0:12:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救赎的准备还没完成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.71,0:12:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样子人类就会毁灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.15,0:12:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不受我控制呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.93,0:12:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有LiNKER的作用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.95,0:12:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,操控权都在我手上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可不会让人类全灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.14,0:12:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我所提倡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最实际的人类救赎方式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.84,0:12:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是为了这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.47,0:12:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而背负罪孽的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:13:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算妳对我动手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.43,0:13:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也改变不了地球所剩无几的时间吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是没用的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回想自己假扮菲妮的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍辱吞声看着吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.67,0:13:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪莲娜...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪莲娜...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.08,0:13:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳就尽情的哭泣吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我回来之后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起想想怎么利用剩余的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翼 妳可以吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翼小姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经习惯独自站上舞台了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:58.04,tsubasa,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Imyuteus amenohabakiri tron
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.75,0:14:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是翼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们的奏者只有一名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后该怎么办...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 Symphogear奏者并不只一名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不打算让失去装备的妳去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出场的不会是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,响...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让俘虏出战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳到底有几份是认真？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.21,0:14:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然全部都是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不喜欢妳这点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.07,0:14:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像妳这样高举正义旗帜的伪善者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:15:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不认为自己做的事情正确...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.82,0:15:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受重伤时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了让家人高兴而努力进行复健
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是从我回到家开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈跟外婆一直过着苦日子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我还是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.86,0:15:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想让我的想法变得虚伪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果变得虚伪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.84,0:15:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就无法牵着别人的手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牵着手...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的这样想？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想要让调妳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做自己想做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.83,0:15:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们目标一致
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.84,0:15:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望妳能够帮助我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想做的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳想做的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.76,0:15:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阻止暴走的伙伴们对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能够拯救大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.29,0:15:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能帮妳们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.59,0:15:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是能相信我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们曾是敌人喔...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.34,0:16:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说什么敌人伙伴的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.14,0:16:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不让小孩子做自己想做的事情大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如就羞耻到死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.68,0:16:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,师傅～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.89,0:16:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.36,0:16:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们还是没变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我们很天真
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这是本性
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我带妳到出发口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点来！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.40,0:16:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,响？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在干嘛啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是有说过不打算让妳出战的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.24,0:16:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是去救人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不记得让妳看过只出张嘴的电影啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.93,0:16:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请让她去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拯救别人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是最像响的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:16:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然像这样横冲直撞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.84,0:17:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本来是我的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.71,0:17:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弦十郎先生吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.49,0:17:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等她回来再教训她吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.41,0:17:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为她准备最好的待遇！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.34,0:17:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们现在...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后方支持就交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会尽全力支持
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能只让小鬼们表现呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.86,0:17:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立花跟那名奏者一起吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.57,0:17:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟预想的一样冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.54,0:17:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上会合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.10,0:17:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noise的补充变慢了呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.19,0:17:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来已经被请出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想也差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.74,0:17:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.95,0:17:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家在那里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我觉得是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.02,0:17:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觉得？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:17:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.51,0:18:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,切歌！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Death！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,切酱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.42,0:18:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,调
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳一定要这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.80,0:18:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以教授的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不会留下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不以教授的做法 什么都不会留下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经没时间了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳们两个冷静点 好好的交谈吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在战场上说什么傻话啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:18:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳先进去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:19:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的话一定能阻止玛丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.77,0:19:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能够牵着她的手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.36,0:19:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,调...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.03,0:19:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我维系装备的LiNKER有限
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以快点走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.02,0:19:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坚信着妳心中的歌声吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坚信着妳心中的歌声吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会让妳得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,调！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.59,0:19:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么帮她啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.32,0:19:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不是妳最讨厌的伪善者吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.87,0:19:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是她不是伪装自己在行动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.59,0:19:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想做就做的她是如此耀眼得让我羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.97,0:19:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我想要相信她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.43,0:19:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.75,0:19:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还是无法让步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.02,0:19:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要在失去自我之前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.96,0:19:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能以某种形式留存下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在切酱失去自我前？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.95,0:19:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,调和玛莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.64,0:19:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有玛姆妳们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.27,0:19:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想把我存在过的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留给妳们！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是理由？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.56,0:20:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是理由Death！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.75,0:20:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这心中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有互相矛盾的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.83,0:20:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还存在着的话！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.28,0:21:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关系那么好的调跟切歌会战斗...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.24,0:21:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这也是我的错吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.92,0:21:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是期望这种事情才做的...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.78,0:21:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛姆！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.76,0:21:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在只有妳一个？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:43.88,Default-eng2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(660,650)}Frontier
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:43.88,Default-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(660,650)}Frontier
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我分析了疆域的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.41,0:21:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到有可能阻止月球冲击的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.74,0:21:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是最后仅剩的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.46,0:21:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.48,0:21:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要妳的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.83,0:21:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的歌声...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要心中还有着歌声！
